{"tid":1764380,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"撞人交通警已復工","createTime":"2019-12-01T05:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T00:58:56.000Z","uid":331421,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eef0e1fc3a9bd2fdc3e37f10a135f78a4ebc67a6","tid":1764380,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:34:37.000Z","msg":"11 月 11 日全港「三罷」期間，有一名交通警於葵芳新都會廣場對出馬路，駕駛警察電單車衝向人群，至少有兩人被撞傷。《立場》早前引述消息指，該警員已經復職。警務處處長鄧炳強今日出席節目無綫節目《講清講楚》時承認涉事警員休假後已復工，但強調調查仍在進行，復職與調查並無關係，否認縱容。<br />\n<br />\n警方早前指事件非常嚴重，時任警察公共關係科總警司謝振中曾指出，涉事的交通警已即時停止在前線工作並休假，將案件交由新界總區調查 ，如發現有違反紀律的行為，會嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士早前向《立場新聞》透露，涉事警員近日已復職，有關事件並非列作交通意外調查，而是列作「交通投訴」，由於至今未有投訴人、證人等，有關警員未有被紀律處分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E8%AD%A6%E9%9B%BB%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E6%92%9E%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4-%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%B2%E5%BE%A9%E8%81%B7-%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E7%B8%B1%E5%AE%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25BE%25A4-%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E8%2581%25B7-%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E5%25AE%25B9%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=e69ba06f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25BE%25A4-%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E8%2581%25B7-%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E5%25AE%25B9%2F&h=5f0e19c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BA%A4%E